---
title: Galaxy Greens Ricotta Ravioli with Zucchini, Toasted Panko & Parsley
description: Channel your inner Groot (or if you’re feeling extra-cute, Baby Groot) and harness the power of plants! We’ve loaded up fresh spinach ricotta ravioli with a luscious tomato cream sauce made with crème fraîche, cream cheese, and a bright squeeze of lemon. Over top there’s lemony zucchini, toasted panko for crunch, and parsley leaves for even more vibrant green on your plate. There’s only one thing left to say about this epic meal: I AM GROOT!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/galaxy-greens-ricotta-ravioli-e3297e97.jpg
